Definition: an illegal scheme for making money by manipulating stock prices
Example: the schemer persuades other people to buy the stock and then sells it himself as soon as the price of the stock rises
Synonyms: contrivance, an, illegal, scheme, for, making, money, by, manipulating, stock, prices, the, schemer, persuades, other, people, to, buy, and, then, sells, it, himself, as, soon, price, of, rises
Category: noun.cognition
